You guys arent that bad but I know that there are some current thoughts from 
people I have talked to that lead me to believe that the council does need a 
taste of fresh meat so to speak. If an election does start up I know I will 
be throwing my hat in and I know that at least one council member thinks I 
should be on the council. After all some of the things I have talked to the 
council about have been met with positive feedback.

--part1_1a5.4f84530.2a5f9190_boundary
